WEBVTT


00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.560
I will look at your votes in the European Parliament.

00:00:02.600 --> 00:00:04.120
Not once have you

00:00:04.440 --> 00:00:06.280
firmly supported Ukraine.

00:00:06.760 --> 00:00:09.200
I look at your votes in the European Parliament too,

00:00:09.480 --> 00:00:10.280
Bardella Garden.

00:00:10.600 --> 00:00:14.400
Not once have you supported the Russian opponent

00:00:14.760 --> 00:00:15.800
Alexa and Nathalie.

00:00:15.880 --> 00:00:16.880
Not once,

00:00:17.280 --> 00:00:18.500
by 6 times, 

00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:19.720
we asked you

00:00:19.960 --> 00:00:23.400
to condemn the conditions of his imprisonment.

00:00:23.840 --> 00:00:27.600
Every 6 times you have refused to condemn these conditions.

00:00:28.040 --> 00:00:29.400
You ended up doing it

00:00:30.520 --> 00:00:31.640
the day after his death.

00:00:33.120 --> 00:00:33.920
And you were there

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:35.920
when his widow came to the European Parliament.

00:00:36.800 --> 00:00:38.800
How you could look her in the eye,

00:00:39.480 --> 00:00:40.280
Yes Barnella ?
